        <main class="policy-container">
            <section class="section-heading">
                <h1>Cookies Policy</h1>
                <p>Effective Date: May 19, 2025</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
                <p>Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device when you visit a website. They are widely used to improve user experience and website functionality.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>2. Why We Use Cookies</h2>
                <p>FlyDreamAir uses cookies to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ensure the website functions properly.</li>
                    <li>Remember your preferences and settings.</li>
                    <li>Improve the speed and security of the website.</li>
                    <li>Analyze website traffic and user behavior.</li>
                    <li>Display personalized content and ads.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>3. Types of Cookies We Use</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for the website to function (e.g. login, navigation).</li>
                    <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> Help us analyze site traffic and improve user experience.</li>
                    <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> Remember your choices and preferences.</li>
                    <li><strong>Marketing Cookies:</strong> Track browsing habits to deliver relevant ads via third-party services.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>4. Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h2>
                <p>You can control or delete cookies at any time via your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may impact your ability to use certain parts of our site.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>5. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
                <p>Some cookies are set by trusted third-party services such as Google Analytics or social media integrations. We do not control these cookies and recommend checking the privacy policies of those services.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>6. Consent</h2>
                <p>By continuing to use our website, you agree to our use of cookies in accordance with this policy. You may opt out or adjust your settings at any time.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this Cookies Policy periodically. The updated version will be posted on this page with the new effective date.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@flydreamair.com">privacy@flydreamair.com</a>.</p>
            </section>
